== Priesthood == He was ordained as a [[Priesthood in the Catholic Church|catholic priest]] on 3 May 1984.
== Episcopate == He was appointed as [[Bishop in the Catholic Church|Bishop]] of [[Bettiah]] on 27 June 1998 and [[ordained]] on 11 November 1998. He was appointed Archbishop of Raipur on 3 July 2013 and installed on 19 September 2013. He has served as Chancellor of the Diocese of Raipur and, as of 2017, is chairman of the education commission of the Bihar Regional Council of Bishops.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://directory.ucanews.com/bishops/archbishop-thakur/731|title=Archbishop Victor Henry Thakur {{!}} Archbishop of Raipur Archdiocese Victor Henry Thakur {{!}} Ucanews|website=directory.ucanews.com|access-date=2017-06-18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bthakur.html|title=Archbishop Victor Henry Thakur [Catholic-Hierarchy]|last=Cheney|first=David M.|website=www.catholic-hierarchy.org|access-date=2017-06-18}}</ref>
